A bunch of TrollStore tools packed into one application. Tools include AirTroller, carrier changer, location simulation, passcode buttons theming, device (un)supervised spoof, etc. This is still in alpha, so expect bugs if you try it
Last updated: 11-29-2023
Status: ❌

Status: ✅

apps.name: iTranslatePro
apps.localizedDescription:
Injected with Pro. Translation and dictionary app making it easy to break language barriers. It allows for easy translation of text, websites, objects, and voice conversations in over 100 languages. Note: Begin by installing it from the App Store, log in, then proceed to force install the TrollStore version. This should grant access to other features like iTranslate keyboard.

Status: ✅ 👍
